description: Demolition of all existing buildings and the redevelopment of the site to provide 808 residential units, comprising 8 residential blocks (Blocks A-H) ranging from 4-storeys (plus basement) to 16-storeys (plus basement) and including 30 townhouses; a gym facility with associated café; 485 car parking spaces (455 of which are within a basement car park); open space and landscaping; plant; cycle parking; servicing and new vehicular access arrangements to Seagrave Road.
